  "title": "A transcendental approach to Koll\\'ar's injectivity theorem",
  "comments": "22 pages; a minor revision of the preprint circulated in January\n  2006, v2: minor modifications, v3: final version, to appear in Osaka J. Math",
  "journal-ref": null,
  "doi": null,
